//
//  YOUR TURN: we have a pair [name, age]. Unify it against the pattern so that
//  \`name\` binds to "ada" and \`age\` to 36, then answer with [age, name] SWAPPED.
//
// GOAL — fix the program so its answers are exactly: [[36, "ada"]]
